Here is a funny Wall Street Journal story about venture capital incentives:

Unable to forget their biggest mistakes, some venture investors=E2=80=94who=
 by definition are mostly investing in companies before they become success=
ful=E2=80=94are embracing them, talking about them, even writing them down.=
