"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0000=
00; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bott=
om-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> to=
 say no thanks</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">As you know, it is our fiduciary obligation to=
 continue to act in a way we believe is in the best interests of the Compan=
y and its shareholders. We have always taken that responsibility very serio=
usly and all of our decisions are guided by this duty. ...</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Although we welcome your participation in the =
launch of a strategic alternatives review process, it is also our unanimous=
 view that your return to the Company at this time, while government invest=
igations into your conduct by the U.S. Attorney=E2=80=99s Office and SEC ar=
e still pending, would not be prudent from a shareholder value perspective.=
 This determination is based on a variety of factors, including non-public =
information the Board has become aware of and the risks to the Company and =
its shareholders of placing a greater spotlight on these issues.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On Dec. 31, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloom=
bergbusiness.com/click/30210082.274519/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZl=
cy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzEwOTE5MDcvMDAwMTE5MzEyNTIzMDAyNzYwL2Q0NDc1MjZkZXg5OTUuaHR=
t/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB5706d264" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"it=
emscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !=
important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-b=
ottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> he disagreed</a>:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There is no rationale for your pos=
ition that my return to the Company =E2=80=9Cwould not be prudent from a sh=
areholder value perspective.=E2=80=9D To the contrary, my return in the con=
text of the media rights negotiations and a potential value maximizing stra=
tegic transaction is necessary precisely from a shareholder value perspecti=
ve because it will allow WWE (as well as any transaction counterparties) to=
 engage in these processes knowing they will have the support of the contro=
lling shareholder.=C2=A0</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On Jan. 5 I guess he got tired of this exchang=
e, so he=C2=A0fired three board members and <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bl=
oombergbusiness.com/click/30210082.274519/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoa=
